<p>
<note resp="#resp2" type="mod" n="0895001" target="#nkr_note_mod_0895001">佛說【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【明】【宮】＊，cf. Śārdūlakarṇa-avadāna. 摩登伽經，舍頭諫太子二十八宿經參照</note>
<note resp="#resp2" type="mod" n="0895002" target="#nkr_note_mod_0895002">安息國三藏【大】，三藏法師【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note type="mod" n="0895003" resp="#resp2" target="#nkr_note_mod_0895003">乞【大】，匃【宮】</note>
<note resp="#resp2" type="mod" n="0895004" target="#nkr_note_mod_0895004">問何字名【大】，隨問名名曰【元】【明】，問阿隨字【宮】</note>
